com.metreeca.rest.handlers.actors

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Delegator
      • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.actors.Generator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler

    public final class Generator
extends Delegator
    Virtual resource generator.

    Handles retrieval requests on the virtual linked data resource identified by the request focus item.

    The response RDF body includes the description of the request target as generated by the virtual model generator.

    Empty generated models are reported with a Response.NotFound status code.

    If the request includes a shape, the response includes also the derived shape actually used in the resource generation process, redacted according to request user roles, Form.relate task, Form.convey mode and Form.detail view.
